sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (SUT)
    participant CS as Central System (Tool)

    Note over CP,CS: Memory State: CertificateInstalled
    Note over CP,CS: OCPP 1.6J (Security Extension)
    Note over CP,CS: Page 107, Table 119

    CS->>CP: 1. GetInstalledCertificateIds.req

    CP-->>CS: 2. GetInstalledCertificateIds.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status should be Accepted

    Note over CS: Only send if the certificate<br/>is not already installed

    CS->>CP: 3. InstallCertificate.req

    CP-->>CS: 4. InstallCertificate.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status should be Accepted

    Note over CP,CS: State is CertificateInstalled
